    "text": [
        "Dear Sir/Madam,",
        "I am writing this letter to bring to your notice that I forgot a watch on the plane EX045, Seat 22 - while flying from Munich to Paris on 15th July, 2022.",
        "I removed the watch while flying and left it on the seat. It is a Rose Gold colour that has some design on the dial and stonework. Since I slept on the plane, the watch might have got under the blanket and gone unnoticed.",
        "The watch was gifted to me by my father at my graduation, which makes it really important. Although I have insurance, it is significant to me as it is the first item purchased by my father to me. So, it holds a lot of emotions and values for me.",
        "I would like to request you to allow your staff to search for my watch on the flight. If found, kindly give me a call at 321-4567-456 or deposit in lost and found.",
        "Yours faithfully,",
        "Patrick."
